name: releases/cpp/v1.4.1
body:
## What's Changed
* Remove dead members in McapReader by @kyle-basis in https://github.com/foxglove/mcap/pull/1199
* cpp: Fix for undefined behavior in mcap::ParseByteArray(..) by @MichaelOrlov in https://github.com/foxglove/mcap/pull/1239

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/foxglove/mcap/compare/releases/cpp/v1.4.0...releases/cpp/v1.4.1

name: @mcap/core v2.1.4
body: Revert of performance improvements in 2.1.3 which broke stream reading.

name: releases/rust/v0.9.0

name: releases/rust/v0.7.1
